***collections, fields and documents***

-> mongosh
-> show dbs
-> use dbName [Even if the database does not exist, it will be created when you insert data]
-> show collections
->db.collectionName.insertOne({"name":"name","age":"12"}) [Even if the collection does not exist, it will be created when you insert data]
->db.collectionName.find() [find all documents in the collection]
->db.collectionName.find({name:"name"}) [find documents with name "name"]
->db.collectionName.deleteOne({name:"name"}) [delete documents with name "name"]





